    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> War sphere, Squadron Commander; or Warleader sphere, Troop Commander.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As a swift action, you may spend a spell point or expend your martial focus and designate a target. Until the beginning of your next turn, whenever a member of your squadron hits that target, all members of your squadron receive an additional +1 circumstance bonus to attack rolls and damage against that target. Members with iterative attacks can benefit from bonuses generated earlier in the same turn. This bonus stacks with itself, up to a maximum equal to your War caster level or your ranks in Diplomacy, whichever is higher.</p>\n",
